他們的競爭力就更強了。希望我能和C.朗拿度在歐冠盃決賽碰面，之後發生什麼我們再看吧。」<br />\n  當被問到誰是世界上最好的球員時，美斯回答：「麥巴比、尼馬、夏薩特、蘇亞雷斯、阿古路。」<br />\n  為什麼沒有C.朗拿度呢？<span style=\"color: red;\">「我會把他和我放在一個級別。我發誓我說的是真心的。」</span><br />\n<br />\n又一個唔識波剩係打開fifa嘅傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T05:22:34.000Z","msg":"你證明咗樓上係條on9<br />\n同時亦證明小花嘅humble<br />\n更加反襯出柒朗嘅自誇自大同目中無人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T23:02:14.000Z","msg":"巴狗球員都成日出黎唔認輸, 全部新聞都google得到"},{"pid":"cfc7188f7ea051252431f412024f00bb22bbf531","tid":1134663,"uid":34336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T23:12:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"804ea9684975ce98f0115c84429342352245a0d6","tid":1134663,"uid":106701,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"3704c4499dd32bba6e8fe56e95e582715c6aa3cd","tid":1134663,"uid":170772,"like":131,"dislike":28,"score":103,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T23:22:40.000Z","msg":"其實大部份球員都知冇得比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />特別係名宿<br />\n就算你睇下身邊啲朗迷<br />\n一係中學雞 一係唔睇波淨係打開fifa"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T23:13:53.000Z","msg":"想問你係邊度波名宿？<br />\n得閒教下我睇波thx"},{"pid":"cba98549e2e05d4f465ec313847b6e49a9611eef","tid":1134663,"uid":137605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"804ea9684975ce98f0115c84429342352245a0d6","tid":1134663,"uid":106701,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"3704c4499dd32bba6e8fe56e95e582715c6aa3cd","tid":1134663,"uid":170772,"like":131,"dislike":28,"score":103,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T23:22:40.000Z","msg":"其實大部份球員都知冇得比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />特別係名宿<br />\n就算你睇下身邊啲朗迷<br />\n一係中學雞 一係唔睇波淨係打開fifa"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T23:13:53.000Z","msg":"想問你係邊度波名宿？<br />\n得閒教下我睇波thx"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T23:14:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ef8e74b78b64a817